rows.label: qst201910_msg0001
rows.name:
We not in wrong! We
just do what we told!

rows.label: qst201910_msg0002
rows.name:
Oh? And what, pray tell, is
it that you were told to do?

rows.label: qst201910_msg0003
rows.name:
Told to bury four barrels in
different places in Alst.

rows.label: qst201910_msg0004
rows.name:
We only bury them, so we
not know what inside!

rows.label: qst201910_msg0005
rows.name:
Interesting... Perhaps we should
give them credit where it's due.

rows.label: qst201910_msg0007
rows.name:
They split the money up to avoid
attracting attention by having a large
sum of money in one place, I gather?

rows.label: qst201910_msg0009
rows.name:
Now, feathered ingrates!
You shall tell us the
location of these barrels!

rows.label: qst201910_msg0010
rows.name:
Okay, okay! Alala tell you now,
so please give some space!

rows.label: qst201910_msg0011
rows.name:
Alala and friends buried barrels...
Near Sauros's Bed in Gula...

rows.label: qst201910_msg0012
rows.name:
Near Leaning Tower of
Dorrick in Temperantia...

rows.label: qst201910_msg0015
rows.name:
Near Wonder Spring Plaza Ruins
in Spirit Crucible Elpys...

rows.label: qst201910_msg0016
rows.name:
And finally near Balquors
Ruins at Cliffs of Mors!

rows.label: qst201910_msg0013
rows.name: Well, friends, you heard the ingrate!

rows.label: qst201910_msg0014
rows.name:
It is time to reclaim the money
that is rightfully ours!
